{
  "stem": "14928.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Probably rumors were going around also that something won't be good here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They didn't know if we would know we would know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he, um-- he took me there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went to the working ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's why I happened to be in the working ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, the same night when the working-- they closed up the ghetto 6 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the evening, there was already Jewish police for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the police, uh, had-- were supposed to take everybody out on the market when it got dark.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They said they're going to have a count at [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everything will be OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All they have to do is count the people, how many people there are.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the first thing, they brought him out to the market.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was in a marketplace, which was all empty-like, and all around were big buildings.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in the middle was nothing because there was a market where people come in with their-- they took out all these people in the market.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they already had their machine guns put up all around.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they-- the same time they just brought them out there, they started shooting.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was a policeman that took out his whole family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because they did not know-- like some people say that the police's fault, it was this fault-- they did not tell them what it's going to be-- not the Jewish police, they didn't tell.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they killed all the people except my friend that worked with me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was hiding in an attic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She didn't care what they said.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They said, come out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If we'll find you, we'll kill you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was from Lodz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was hiding by herself in the attic in the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
